rding to authorities, the shooting left one 18-year-old student dead and 7 others injured. The youngest victim is 15 years old. "SOURCES: Reuters, CNNhttps://www.reuters.com/article/us-colorado-shooting-idUSKCN1SD2H2https://edition.cnn.com/2019/05/07/us/colorado-denver-area-school-shooting/index.html***]]></description>
